parameters.description:
Specifies scenario which will be used to filter user sessions:
Use LoggedIn option to filter user sessions that were active (logged in) within the specified time range (default option);
Use Created option to filter user sessions that were created within the specified time range

emailRecipients.description:
Gets or sets the list of email recipients for the health alert notifications.
This should be a comma-separated list of email addresses.
